{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vividerie is a hard bullet hell roguelike that has you shoot, dash and magic your way through hordes of vile creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight your way through the dungeons, unearth powerful relics, and find yummy burger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tough, Precise Action</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vividerie is designed for those who crave a difficult game;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No mistake goes unpunished, but great feats are rewarded just as much.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master complex mechanics, learn to dodge overwhelming patterns, and brew ridiculous builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Roguelike Adventuring</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No two runs are ever the same, with 3 dungeons (More coming soon!) and fresh layouts every time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find special rooms that drastically alter the course of your adventure, and find secrets within their cracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wild Synergies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover over 100 items and combine them in myriads of ways to wreak havoc upon your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Figure out ridiculous amalgamations of stat modifiers, effects, and proc-chains that can make or break a run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Press/Creator Asset Kit:<br></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769200/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729806988","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769200/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729806988","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769200/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729806988","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i